Class Solver

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mills.cs114.lab8.Solver

  • public class Solver
extends java.lang.Object
    A "solver" that tries to find a sequence of transitions from a given State to an accept state in a nondeterministic finite automaton (NFA).
    Author:
    Ellen Spertus
